01:19:33.565 --> 01:19:35.157
The truck, the truck, the truck!

01:19:35.234 --> 01:19:36.360
Come on, Paloma!

01:19:39.037 --> 01:19:40.026
Hurry!

01:19:41.907 --> 01:19:43.704
¡Caramba!

01:19:43.775 --> 01:19:45.504
