because she's so rich.

01:20:10.369 --> 01:20:12.234
I hope so, Paloma.

01:20:12.304 --> 01:20:14.169
I hope that's all it is.

01:20:17.409 --> 01:20:18.876
Drive fast!

01:20:27.952 --> 01:20:30.147
